;=======================================================================================================================
```	Every 1/50th (PAL) or 1/60th (NTSC) of a second, an interrupt is generated and control passes here.
        There's only a small amount of space between this routine and the pause handler, so we just jump to the
        routine proper.
	```
.ORG	$0038
	;---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        jp      interruptHandler
	;

